30:28.160 --> 30:33.560
have something else that's profound, which is the ability to bond so completely one-on-one

30:33.560 --> 30:35.000
with their companion.

30:35.000 --> 30:42.480
So it's that bond that works in a very deep way to help them unwind the symptoms of PTSD.

30:42.480 --> 30:47.240
It's just an absolute unconditional love that those dogs feel one-on-one.

30:47.240 --> 30:52.080
Now any dog can feel that, but in a service dog when you combine it with so many other

30:52.080 --> 30:56.680
things, it's a profound therapeutic tool.

30:56.680 --> 30:57.680
It's very powerful.

30:57.680 --> 31:00.800
