you to and make you feel better because of course when you pet a dog or look into the

35:24.560 --> 35:30.920
eyes of a dog there's an oxytocin release and it feels good so it's a very very powerful

35:30.920 --> 35:34.800
connection that happens with a bonded animal and a human.

35:34.800 --> 35:37.440
My dogs love it when I'm sick in bed all day.

